{"tid":945432,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傑斯撐摩佬：球員拉低紅魔水準","createTime":"2018-12-18T01:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T11:09:57.000Z","uid":122,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"227820eb1103261ebcbf509fd6077e7f1267178f","tid":945432,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:29:00.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=LTtkzNEE4HXdLZFdqzpenTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=7cf85d44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯領隊摩連奴喪師雙紅會後，不少名宿皆高聲批評，傳奇左翼傑斯就出言維護。<br />\n<br />\n「在漫長的球季之中，你可以在這些賽事落敗。以往曼聯贏得聯賽時，我們也曾於晏菲路落敗，也曾在奧脫福不敵。可是，今季明顯令人失望，所以被宿敵擊敗，球迷肯定不高興。」傑斯（Ryan Giggs）表示。<br />\n<br />\n當大部份評論都炮轟摩連奴時，傑斯繼續力撐這名葡萄牙籍名帥，認為球員責任最大：「摩佬受到很多批評，有對有錯，但球員才應該負責任。他不是在場上失去控制的人，他不是像安達靴里拉向沙迪奧文尼作愚蠢攔截的人。」<br />\n<br />\n這名威爾斯代表隊領隊認為，曼聯一直都是高水準，現在這些球員把它拉低了：「我們看到盧卡古、保羅普巴於世界盃的表現，踢出了最高水準，回到球會卻未能延續。紅魔以19分落後利物浦，但肯定不是比對方差19分。」"},{"pid":"922aaa92065d9576edbfce32b32fb302bce88805","tid":945432,"uid":35508,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:25:57.000Z","msg":"是但啦 永續摩daddy la diu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1319dc3be528bc02cc9487ad838ee97a310607bd","tid":945432,"uid":39027,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:28:52.000Z","msg":"紅魔以19分落後利物浦，但肯定不是比對方差19分。<br />\n<br />\n瘋了  全都瘋了"},{"pid":"5d1252a80208fdf9c5a08ff36013c53a5d213d9e","tid":945432,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:58:13.000Z","msg":"其實傑斯教最岩"},{"pid":"7ee481eb24ad496f795f71047fcc2671163b736b","tid":945432,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:14:52.000Z","msg":"摩佬 又加1分"},{"pid":"e20d64568eb707a505eedde881b89aeaae4d0f91","tid":945432,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:14:14.000Z","msg":"他不是像安達靴里拉向沙迪奧文尼作愚蠢攔截的人。<br />\n<br />\n開名屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f370da7347fb221f9460f2559e231b68130a1a","tid":945432,"uid":100766,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:21:40.000Z","msg":"啲獌狗名縮睇野真係好撚獨特<br />\n做到眾人皆醒佢地獨醉咁<br />\n仲要係麻醉嗰隻<br />\n<br />\n永續摩狗啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be008a8e3338735d13a7c60d12a711a0c47ca9ac","tid":945432,"uid":13504,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:24:01.000Z","msg":"你手頭上有世界級球員你唔識用唔識提升佢地狀態<br />\n咁中下遊果D領隊點搞? 球員本身已經唔係世界級,咁係唔係一開波要投降拎呢個做藉口唔洗踢呀"},{"pid":"aae296bb38782a45c3d81339f1b580b0d878276f","tid":945432,"uid":189900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:31:01.000Z","msg":"Sick波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b259ba827f7244cca049b152d66161f203fcb2","tid":945432,"uid":56467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:41:06.000Z","msg":"R撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea1f8ec91d5ee07285a5c2e20cc898aa2f3a6b5","tid":945432,"uid":59731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:22:59.000Z","msg":"咁強曼聯長老都撐魔佬，你班死獌狗仲反摩？用下個豬腦諗下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944602232ad4dd1a3cf07482e7b3a8d2105b703a","tid":945432,"uid":59731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fea1f8ec91d5ee07285a5c2e20cc898aa2f3a6b5","tid":945432,"uid":59731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:22:59.000Z","msg":"咁強曼聯長老都撐魔佬，你班死獌狗仲反摩？用下個豬腦諗下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:23:42.000Z","msg":"咁多曼聯長老都